quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,105,Yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen fenni Nulaa…ďe …ďen
  26,106,"Tuma nde Nuuhu musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on wi'annoo …ďe: \"Enee, on hulataa [Alla]"
  26,107,"Min dey, ko mi Nulaa…óo e moo…óon hoolaa…óo"
  26,108,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,109,"Mi toraaki on e dow …óum njo…ďdi, njo…ďdi am ndin fawaaki si wanaa Jooma winndere nden"
  26,110,Hulee Alla …óofto…óon mi
  26,111,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Enee, hara men gom…óinte, jaasu…ďe …ďen no jokkumaa"
  26,112,"O maaki: \"Ko hon…óum woni ganndal am e ko …ďe wonunoo e gollude"
  26,113,"Hasboore ma…ď…ďe nden fawaaki si wanaa e Joomi am, sinndo hi…óon so'aynoo"
  26,114,Min mi wonaali ra…óotoo…óo gom…óin…ďe …ďen
  26,115,Min mi wonaali si wanaa jertinoowo …ďanngu…óo
  26,116,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Men woondii si a accaali an Nuuhu, ma a laato sanne jeyaa…óo e rajmetee…ďe …ďen"
  26,117,"O maaki: \"Joom am, pellet, yim…ďe am …ďen …ďe fenni lam"
  26,118,"√Ďaawu hakkunde am e ma…ď…ďe √Īaawoore, danndaa mi e …ďen wonndu…ďe e am jeyaa…ďe e gom…óin…ďe …ďen"
  26,119,Men danndi mo e …ďen wonndu…ďe e makko ka nder laana ∆īoltiika(loowaaka)
  26,120,"Refti Men yooli …ďaawo [ma…ď…ďe] heddii…ďe …ďen"
  26,121,"Pellet, wonii e …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aaya, …ďur…ďe heewude e ma…ď…ďe laataaki gom…óin…ďe"
  26,122,"Pellet, Joomi maa…óa, ko Kanko woni Teddu…óo Yurmetee…óo"